Usage: changeBBoxMasterFromR0 [-help] <cellName>
                              {R90 R180 R270 MX MX90 MY MY90} <newOriginX>
                              <newOriginY>

-help                               # Prints out the command usage
<cellName>                          # Specifies the name of the black box cell
                                    # (string, required)
{R90 R180 R270 MX MX90 MY MY90}     # Specifies new orientation of cell
                                    # (enum, required)
<newOriginX>                        # Specifies the new origin x-ordinate
                                    # (float, required)
<newOriginY>                        # Specifies the new origin y-ordinate
                                    # (float, required)